# Styling — Mantine + SCSS Modules

## No Tailwind. No CSS-in-JS.

This project uses Mantine v7 + SCSS Modules. Do NOT introduce Tailwind, styled-components, Emotion, or CSS-in-JS.

## Mantine Theme (`src/app/style/`)

- `theme.ts` — `createTheme()` with custom font, colors, scale
- `colors.ts` — `Colors` static class with 60+ named constants
- Font: `Figtree, sans-serif`
- Primary color: `primaryPurple` (#331062)
- Scale: `1.6`
- **Light mode only**: `forceColorScheme="light"` — no dark mode

## Styling Priority (Use In This Order)

1. **Mantine component props** — `p="md"`, `bg="gray.1"`, `c="dimmed"`, `fz="sm"` for simple spacing/colors
2. **Mantine `classNames` prop** — override component internals with SCSS module classes
3. **SCSS Modules** — `*.module.scss` co-located with component, for layout and custom styling
4. **Inline `style={{}}`** — ONLY for truly dynamic values computed at runtime (transforms, positions from drag operations)

## Color Tokens

```typescript
import { Colors } from '@/app/style/colors';
// Colors.primaryColor    → #331062
// Colors.lightGrey       → #F5F5F5
// Colors.emeraldGreen    → #50C878
```

**Never hardcode hex values** — always reference `Colors.xxx` or Mantine theme tokens. If a new color is needed, add it to `Colors` class first.

## SCSS Modules

```typescript
import styles from './Component.module.scss';
<div className={styles.container}>
```

- One `.module.scss` per component directory
- Use `camelCase` class names: `.headerContainer`, not `.header-container`
- Nest selectors sparingly — max 3 levels deep

## PostCSS Breakpoints

Available via `postcss-simple-vars`:

```scss
@media (max-width: $mantine-breakpoint-sm) { /* 48em */ }
@media (max-width: $mantine-breakpoint-md) { /* 62em */ }
```

Breakpoints: xs=36em, sm=48em, md=62em, lg=75em, xl=88em. **No hardcoded px media queries.**

## Anti-Patterns

```tsx
// BAD: Inline style for static values (100+ instances exist — do not add more)
<div style={{ display: 'flex', gap: '8px', padding: '16px' }}>

// GOOD: SCSS Module
<div className={styles.flexRow}>

// BAD: Raw hex in component
<Text c="#331062">Title</Text>

// GOOD: Color token
<Text c={Colors.primaryColor}>Title</Text>

// BAD: Hardcoded breakpoint
@media (max-width: 768px) { }

// GOOD: Mantine variable
@media (max-width: $mantine-breakpoint-sm) { }
```

## Shift Colors

Roster shift color codes: `@/utils/rosterShiftColorCodes.ts` — do not duplicate or hardcode shift colors.
